ing%20to%20influence%20global%20politics%20through%20his%20Open%20Society%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-explains-how-sam-pirodas-remarks-stem-from-a-colonial-mindset-5631036%5C%22%3ES%20Jaishankar%20Says%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20Remarks%20Stem%20From%20A%20'Colonial%20Mindset'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20among%20the%20US'%20major%20headaches%20in%20view%20of%20security%20concerns%20and%20trade%20implications.%20India%20too%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20border%20dispute%20with%20China%2C%20which%20was%20marked%20by%20violent%20clashes%20in%202020.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20disengagement%20process%20and%20military-level%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20in%20India%20claims%20the%20country%20had%20lost%20a%20chunk%20of%20its%20land%20to%20China%20during%20these%20clashes%20-%20a%20claim%20that%20resurfaced%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20parliament%20speech%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20claimed%20China%20has%20control%20over%204%2C000%20sq%20km%20of%20Indian%20territory%2C%20which%20was%20refuted%20by%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESam%20Pitroda's%20Controversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20has%20courted%20controversies%20in%20the%20past%20well.%20His%20comments%20in%202024%20on%20the%20diversity%20among%20Indians%20were%20seen%20as%20racist%20and%20even%20drew%20backlash%20from%20PM%20Modi.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20had%20stood%20by%20his%20remarks%20and%20blamed%20it%20on%20the%20words%20that%20he%20chose%20to%20express%20himself.%20The%20Congress%20had%20distanced%20itself%20from%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20uproar%2C%20he%20had%20given%20up%20his%20post%20of%20Congress%20overseas%20chief%20but%20was%20back%20at%20the%20helm%20after%20seven%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sparked