3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-today-delhi-residents-on-strong-earthquake-tremors-never-felt-like-this-7727406%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNever%20Felt%20Like%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20Delhi%20Residents%20On%20Strong%20Earthquake%20Tremors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20residents%20claimed%20they%20were%20panicked%20seeing%20the%20buildings%20shaking%20while%20a%20passenger%20at%20a%20railway%20station%20said%20he%20felt%20that%20a%20train%20was%20running%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EDelhi%20In%20Seismic%20Zone%20IV%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20earthquakes%20are%20not%20unusual%20in%20Delhi%20due%20to%20its%20geographic%20location.%20The%20city%20has%20frequently%20witnessed%20such%20tremors%20in%20the%20past%20-%20in%202020%2C%20at%20least%20three%20earthquakes%20above%203.0%20magnitude%20hit%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20dozen%20aftershocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20is%20located%20in%20the%20Seismic%20Zone%204%20which%20has%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20earthquakes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority.%20This%20zone%20has%20a%20fairly%20high%20seismicity%20where%20earthquakes%20generally%20occur%20in%20the%20range%20of%205-6%20magnitude%2C%20and%20even%207-8%20occasionally.%20The%20zoning%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20that%20keeps%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-today-pm-narendra-modi-urges-calm-after-strong-tremors-hit-delhi-ghaziabad-gurgaon-faridabad-7727475%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BStay%20Alert%20For%20Possible%20Aftershocks%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20On%20Delhi%20Earthquake%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201720%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20at%20least%20five%20earthquakes%20above%205.5%20magnitude%20on%20the%20Richter%20scale%2C%20reports%20suggest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earth's%20crust%20-%20the%20thin%20outermost%20layer%20-%20is%20made%20of%20large%20and%20solid%20slabs%20of%20rock%20known%20as%20tectonic%20plates.%20There%20are%20about%20seven%20major%20and%20minor%20such%20plates.%20These%20plates%20move%20very%20slowly%2C%20causing%20deformations%20that%20lead%20to%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20India%2C%20including%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20collision%20of%20the%20Indian%20tectonic%20plate%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20plate%20contributes%20to%20seismicity%20or%20the%20frequency%20of%20earthquakes.%20These%20plates%20store%20energy%20like%20a%20spring%20and%20when%20they%20slip%20above%20one%20another%2C%20it%20releases%20the%20energy%20and%20results%20in%20an%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeismicity%20around%20Delhi%20appears%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20a%20major%20geological%20structure%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Delhi-Hardwar%20Ridge.%20It%20coincides%20with%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Aravali%20Mountain%20belt%20beneath%20the%20alluvial%20plains%20of%20the%20Ganga%20basin%20to%20the%20northeast%20of%20Delhi%20towards%20the%20Himalayan%20mountain%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20DDMA%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20Saturday's%20earthquake%2C%20asserted%20NCS%20director%20OP%20Mishra%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20not%20caused%20due%20to%20any%20plate%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20Earthquakes%20Make%20Delhi%20Unsafe%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Delhi's%20location%20in%20Seismic%20Zone%20IV%2C%20a%20SWOT%20analysis%20by%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(NDMA)%20has%20found%20that%20the%20national%20capital%20also%20faces%20threats%20due%20to%20the%20high%20number%20of%20non-earthquake%20resilient%20buildings%2C%20high%20population%20density%2C%20unplanned%20and%20unsafe%20structures%20and%20congested%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Vulnerability%20Atlas%20of%20India%20(1997)%2C%20for%20shaking%20intensity%20VIII%2C%20Delhi%20has%20a%20high%20damage%20risk%20for%206.5%25%20of%20houses%20and%20a%20moderate%20damage%20risk%20for%20over%2085%25%20of%20houses.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fddma.delhi.gov.in%2Fddma%2Fearthquakes%5C%22%3EDDMA%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20these%20estimates%20are%20made%20on%20simplistic%20assumptions%20and%20further%20study%20is%20needed%20to%20understand%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20different%20types%20of%20constructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DDMA%20notes%20that%20an%20earthquake%20disaster%20would%20have%20huge%20economic%20and%20political%20implications%20-%20beyond%20the%20statistics%20of%20deaths%20and%20injuries.%20The%20agency%20says%20that%20though%20the%20city%20cannot%20rule%20out%20a%20possible%20disaster%2C%20it%20can%20sustain%20strong%20tremors%20due%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%26quot%3B%20geological%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20most%20buildings%20in%20Delhi%20may%20not%20meet%20Indian%20standards%20on%20aseismic%20constructions%20and%20may%20be%20considered%20deficient%20from%20a%20seismic%20safety%20viewpoint.%20Thus%2C%20there%20is%20a%20real%20potential%20for%20a%20great%20earthquake%20disaster%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20implications%20of%20which%20go%20well%20beyond%20casualties%20because%20of%20its%20political%20and%20commercial%20significance%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20DDMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739777100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fma45206_india-gate_625x300_28_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-4-magnitude-geography-behind-why-delhi-faces-high-risk-of-earthquakes-seismic-zones-7727957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20strong%20earthquake%20hit%20Delhi%20early%20this%20morning%20and%20the%20tremors%20were%20felt%20across%20north%20India.%2