)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDOGE%2Fstatus%2F1890849405932077378%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20dug%20into%20the%20data%20and%20followed%20the%20trail%20of%20money.%20All%20data%20has%20been%20sourced%20from%20US%20government%20sites%2C%20from%20Income%20Tax%20returns%20and%20the%20websites%20of%20the%20NGOs%20involved%20in%20funneling%20money%20to%20India%20for%20%26quot%3Bvoter%20turnout%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20get%20into%20the%20details%2C%20let's%20look%20at%20why%20this%20is%20significant.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20been%20under%20fire%20since%20Donald%20Trump%20took%20over%20as%20President%20in%20January.%20President%20Trump%20has%20alleged%20large-scale%20corruption%20in%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6MGaxjbHUz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6MGaxjbHUz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Donald%20J.%20Trump%20(%40realDonaldTrump)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1887916006523166886%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20hinted%20at%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20interference%20in%20regime%20change%20operations%20in%20Europe%20while%20speaking%20at%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20on%20February%2014.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20that%20I%20worry%20about%20the%20most%20vis-a-vis%20Europe%2C%20it's%20not%20Russia%2C%20it's%20not%20China%2C%20it's%20not%20any%20other%20external%20actor.%20And%20what%20I%20worry%20about%20is%20the%20threat%20from%20within.%20The%20retreat%20of%20Europe%20from%20some%20of%20its%20most%20fundamental%20values%2C%20values%20shared%20with%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%20I%20was%20struck%20that%20a%20former%20European%20Commissioner%20went%20on%20television%20recently%20and%20sounded%20delighted%20that%20the%20Romanian%20government%20(sic)%20had%20just%20annulled%20an%20entire%20election.%20He%20warned%20that%20if%20things%20don't%20go%20to%20plan%2C%20the%20very%20same%20thing%20could%20happen%20in%20Germany%20too.%20Now%20these%20cavalier%20statements%20are%20shocking%20to%20American%20ears.%20For%20years%20we've%20been%20told%20that%20everything%20we%20fund%20and%20support%20is%20in%20the%20name%20of%20our%20shared%20democratic%20values.%20Everything%20from%20our%20Ukraine%20policy%20to%20digital%20censorship%20is%20billed%20as%20a%20defence%20of%20democracy.%20But%20when%20we%20see%20European%20courts%20cancelling%20elections%2C%20and%20seen%20your%20officials%20threatening%20to%20cancel%20others%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20whether%20we%20are%20holding%20ourselves%20to%20an%20appropriately%20high%20standard.%20And%20I%20say%20ourselves%2C%20because%20I%20fundamentally%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20on%20the%20same%20team.%20We%20must%20do%20more%20than%20talk%20about%20democratic%20values.%20We%20must%20live%20them.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpCOsgfINdKg%3Fsi%3D65cUC_mh-k3OmKHp%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20backdrop%20that%20this%20development%20assumes%20significance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20that%20arises%2C%20once%20we%20delve%20into%20the%20data%2C%20is%20why%20the%20Biden%20administration%20funneled%20so%20much%20money%20via%20USAID%20and%20other%20departments%20to%20NGOs%20that%20worked%20in%20foreign%20countries