rnational%20Foundation%20for%20Electoral...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPO13Iyroee%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPO13Iyroee%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgdgAQoDbPh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgdgAQoDbPh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Malviya%20(%40amitmalviya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1890989529781215669%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%2C%20however%2C%20provided%20a%20response%20to%20PTI%20which%20is%20reproduced%20here%20in%20full%20-%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20in%20a%20section%20of%20Media%20about%20an%20MoU%20by%20ECI%20in%202012%20when%20I%20was%20CEC%2C%20for%20funding%20of%20certain%20million%20dollars%20by%20a%20US%20agency%20for%20raising%20voter%20turnout%20in%20India%20does%20not%20have%20an%20iota%20of%20fact.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYes%2C%20there%20was%20a%20MOU%20with%20IFES%20in%202012%20when%20I%20was%20CEC%20like%20we%20had%20with%20many%20other%20agencies%20and%20Election%20Management%20Bodies%20to%20facilitate%20training%20for%20desirous%20countries%20at%20ECI%20's%20training%20and%20resource%20centre%2C%20IIIDEM%2C%20which%20was%20very%20new%20at%20that%20stage.%20There%20was%20no%20financing%20or%20even%20promise%20of%20finance%20involved%20in%20MoU%2C%20forget%20X%20or%20Y%20amount.%20The%20MoU%20in%20fact%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20black%20and%20white%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20financial%20and%20legal%20obligation%20of%20any%20kind%20on%20either%20side.%20%C2%A0This%20stipulation%20was%20made%20at%20two%20different%20places%20to%20leave%20no%20scope%20for%20any%20ambiguity.%20Any%20mention%20of%20any%20funds%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20MoU%20is%20completely%20false%20and%20malicious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Quraishi's%20statement.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDI%20has%20on%20its%20website%2C%20a%20distorted%20map%20of%20India%20which%20shows%20Kashmir%20as%20not%20being%20part%20of%20India.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20on%20its%20%3Cu%3E%3Ca%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%2217%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22Verified%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ndi.org%252Fwho-we-are%26data%3D05%257C02%257CNonikaM%2540ndtv.com%257C86506ec0b41e45730ed808dd4f1aa0ae%257C89e0013190cd478790cc5ded788d77de%257C0%257C0%257C638753697994394482%257CUnknown%257CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%253D%253D%257C0%257C%257C%257C%26sdata%3Dck6D3dY9Um%252FpSJfFUE7HCPkUuWlPnN1iivZoAk8fO3k%253D%26reserved%3D0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Original%20URL%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndi.org%2Fwho-we-are.%20Click%20or%20tap%20if%20you%20trust%20this%20link.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoard%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20a%20number%20of%20former%20USAID%20employees%20as%20well%20as%20former%20Ambassadors%20and%20people%20who%20have%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20spy%20agency%20CIA.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangkok-based%20ANFREL%2C%20which%20receives%20funding%20from%20NDI%2C%20continues%20to%20move%20the%20money%20forward%20to%20a%20host%20of%20Asian%20nations%2C%20including%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EANFREL's%20%26quot%3Bmissions%26quot%3B%20in%20countries%20like%20Myanmar%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Timor%20Leste%20and%20Nepal%2C%20among%20others%2C%20have%20been%20active%20with%20election%20related%20activities.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%20upon%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20probe%20into%20these%20agencies%20and%20Indian%20entities%20associated%20with%20them%20to%20find%20out%20the%20complete%20truth.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739776800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ffeqvjdso_delhi-voting-ia