ake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20Delhi%20and%20its%20adjoining%20areas%20woke%20up%20to%20strong%20tremors%20caused%20by%20an%20earthquake%20of%20magnitude%204.0%20this%20morning.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Centre%20of%20Seismology%2C%20the%20quake%20hit%20at%20a%20depth%20of%20about%205%20km.%20Videos%20showed%20the%20ground%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearthquake-today-delhi-earthquake-video-shows-moment-4-0-magnitude-earthquake-hit-delhi-ncr-7728059%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuildings%20shaking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forcing%20people%20to%20rush%20out%20of%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20no%20reports%20of%20casualties%20or%20damage%20to%20properties%2C%20but%20many%20residents%20claimed%20that%20the%20tremors%20were%20so%20strong%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20bridge%20was%20collapsing.%20However%2C%20the%20quake%20itself%20was%20not%20of%20a%20high-intensity%20magnitude.%20Generally%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-today-live-updates-4-0-magnitude-earthquake-hits-capital-tremors-felt-across-north-india-earthquake-today-7727335%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearthquake%3C%2Fa%3E%20below%202.5%20magnitude%20does%20not%20cause%20tremors%2C%20a%20quake%20between%202.5%20to%205.4%20magnitude%20leads%20to%20minor%20tremors%20without%20any%20damage.%20Any%20quake%20higher%20than%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20cause%20strong%20tremors%20and%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%20why%20did%20the%204.0%20magnitude%20earthquake%20in%20Delhi%20feel%20so%20strong%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20reasons%20behind%20this%2C%20mainly%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20quake%20was%20Delhi%20itself.%20According%20to%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20(USGS)%2C%20an%20earthquake's%20most%20intense%20shaking%20is%20often%20felt%20near%20the%20epicentre.%20However%2C%20the%20vibrations%20can%20still%20be%20felt%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20away%20from%20it.%20The%20Dhuala%20Kuan%20area%20-%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fdelhi-earthquake-today-strong-earthquake-in-delhi-ncr-sparks-meme-fest-7727824%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepicentre%20of%20today's%20quake%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20has%20been%20experiencing%20smaller%2C%20low-magnitude%20earthquakes%20once%20every%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20It%20had%20recorded%20an%20earthquake%20of%203.3%20magnitude%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20intense%20tremors%20is%20that%20the%20quake%20was%20a%20shallow-depth%20earthquake.%20Generally%2C%20shallow%20earthquakes%2C%20originating%20five%20or%2010%20kilometres%20below%20the%20surface%2C%20tend%20to%20cause%20more%20damage%20than%20those%20originating%20deep%20below%20the%20surface.%20This%20also%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearthquake-today-delhi-earthquake-delhi-residents-report-a-loud-sound-during-earthquake-what-it-is-7728454%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloud%20grumbling%20sound%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20quake.%20The%20USGC%20said%20that%20high-frequency%20vibrations%20from%20shallow%20earthquakes%20generate%20a%20booming%20sound%20as%20the%20ground%20vibrates%20and%20creates%20a%20short-period%20seismic%20wave%20motion%20that%20reaches%20the%20air%20and%20becomes%20sound%20waves.%20The%20shallower%20the%20epicentre%2C%20the%20more%20energy%20and%20sound%20can%20be%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sometimes%2C%20earthquakes%20can%20create%20booming%20sounds%20even%20when%20no%20vibrations%20are%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%2C%20being%20a%20densely%20populated%20city%2C%20also%20led%20to%20strong%20tremors%20as%20the%20seismic%20waves%20travel%20a%20shorter%20distance%20and%20reach%20the%20structures%20faster%20in%20such%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20is%20also%20prone%20to%20earthquakes%20as%20it%20is%20located%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-4-magnitude-geography-behind-why-delhi-faces-high-risk-of-earthquakes-seismic-zones-7727957%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeismic%20Zone%20IV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20this%20zone%20has%20a%20fairly%20high%20seismicity%20where%20earthquakes%20generally%20occur%20in%20the%20range%20of%205-6%20magnitude%2C%20and%20even%207-8%20occasionally.%20The%20zoning%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20that%20keeps%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeismicity%20in%20North%20India%2C%20including%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20is%20due%20to%20the%20collision%20of%20the%20Indian%20plate%20with%20the%20Eurasian%20plate.%20These%20colliding%20plates%20flex%2C%20and%20store%20energy%20like%20a%20spring%2C%20and%20when%20the%20plate's%20margin%20finally%20slips%20to%20release%20energy%2C%20an%20earthquake%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Nothing%20to%20worry'%3A%20Expert%20on%20Delhi%20earthquake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20of%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Seismology%2C%20Dr%20OP%20Mishra%20has%20assured%20residents%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20as%20aftershocks%20of%20lesser%20magnitude%20are%20%26quot%3Bnatural%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20has%20been%20experiencing%20minor%20earthquakes.%20This%20earthquake%20occurred%20in%20Dhaula%20Kuan.%20In%202007%2C%20an%20earthquake%20of%204.7%20magnitude%20had%20occurred%20there.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about.%20It%20is%20a%20seismic%20zone%20there...The%20earthquake%20occurred%20due%20to%20in-situ%20material%20heterogeneity.%20After%204.0%20magnitude%2C%20the%20aftershock%20will%20be%20less%20by%201.2%20magnitudes%2C%20it%20is%20natural%20as%20it%20will%20heal%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739775840000%2C%22visual%22%