0its%20post%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20unit%20also%20highlighted%20that%20the%20drones%20were%20funded%20by%20civilians.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20unit%20of%20a%20Ukrainian%20brigade%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%20said%20it%20destroyed%20three%20advanced%20Russian%20air%20defense%20systems%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ronin%20company%20of%20the%2065th%20Mechanized%20Rifle%20Brigade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FRonins44_65%2F453%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20first-person%20view%20drone%20attacks%20on%20Saturday%2C%20saying%20it%20took%20out%20a%20Tor-M2%2C%20a%20Buk-M2%2C%20and%20a%20Buk-M3.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20some%20of%20Moscow's%20most%20prized%20mobile%20surface-to-air%20missile%20systems%2C%20with%20the%20Tor-M2%20lauded%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fdefense%2F1580769%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20state%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcutting-edge%26quot%3B%20weapon%20that%20can%20counter%20drone%20swarms%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20range%20of%20about%207.5%20miles%2C%20the%20Tor-M2%20is%20designed%20to%20engage%20up%20to%2048%20targets%20at%20once%20at%20low%20to%20medium%20altitudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Buk-M3%20is%20also%20one%20of%20Russia's%20newest%20air%20defenses.%20Russian%20state%20media%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fdefense%2F1580769%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETASS%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompared%20it%20in%202016%20to%20the%20Medium%20Extended%20Air%20Defense%20System%2C%20a%20Western-made%20system%20meant%20to%20replace%20the%20Patriot.%20Each%20Patriot%20system%20is%20estimated%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-patriot-missile-defense-system-cost-middle-east-syria-iraq-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20about%20%241.1%20billion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clips%20posted%20by%20the%20Ronin%20company%20on%20Saturday%20showed%20first-person%20view%20drones%20closely%20approaching%20the%20air%20defense%20systems%20before%20their%20video%20feeds%20went%20dark.%20While%20the%20drones'%20flight%20trajectory%20and%20distance%20to%20the%20Russian%20defenses%20indicate%20a%20successful%20hit%2C%20Business%20Insider%20couldn't%20independently%20verify%20if%20the%20systems%20were%20actively%20deployed%20assets%20or%20were%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20videos%20show%20yet%20another%20example%20of%20how%20the%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20increasingly%20relying%20on%20cheap%20loitering%20munitions%2C%20even%20to%20counter%20high-value%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-drone-makers-producing-fiber-optic-weapons-didnt-think-possible-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrone%20makers%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20usually%20tell%20BI%20that%20they%20sell%20or%20create%20exploding%20drones%20for%20%24750%20to%20%241%2C500%20apiece%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20device's%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20pinpoint%20how%20much%20Russia%20spends%20on%20its%20air%20defense%20systems.%20The%20Ukrainian%20military%20has%20estimated%20that%20the%20Tor-M2%20costs%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fusf_army%2F287%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2427%20million%20per%20unit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20the%20Buk-M3%20costs%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGeneralStaffZSU%2F18121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2440%20to%20%2450%20million%20per%20unit.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ronin%20company's%20post%20on%20Saturday%20also%20indicated%20that%20the%20drones%20used%20in%20the%20attack%20weren't%20officially%20supplied%20but%20received%20through%20civilian%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sponsor%20of%20the%20defeat%20is%20the%20Sternenko%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unit%20wrote%20on%20its%20social%20media%2