's%20quake%20-%20has%20been%20experiencing%20smaller%2C%20low-magnitude%20earthquakes%20once%20every%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20It%20had%20recorded%20an%20earthquake%20of%203.3%20magnitude%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EResidents%20recount%20earthquake%20tremors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-earthquake-today-delhi-residents-on-strong-earthquake-tremors-never-felt-like-this-7727406%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearthquake%20tremors%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewoke%20the%20national%20capital%20up%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20with%20residents%20describing%20the%20moment%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20insane%20earthquakes%26quot%3B.%20Several%20videos%20also%20showed%20the%20moment%20the%20earthquake%20hit%20the%20national%20capital.%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20terrace%20camera%20of%20a%20house%20in%20Delhi%20showed%20tank%20pipes%20and%20wires%20moving%20with%20heavy%20intensity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20passenger%20waiting%20for%20his%20train%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20station%20described%20the%20tremors%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbridge%20collapse%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20waiting%20lounge.%20All%20rushed%20out%20from%20there.%20It%20felt%20as%20if%20any%20bridge%20or%20something%20had%20collapsed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTremors%20were%20so%20strong.%20Felt%20like%20a%20train%20was%20moving%20nearby.%20Everything%20was%20shaking.%20I%20have%20never%20felt%20like%20this%20ever%20before.%20The%20entire%20building%20was%20shaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20quake%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20urged%20citizens%20to%20call%20the%20emergency%20112%20helpline%20for%20emergencies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20you%20all%20are%20safe%2C%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739770980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.c