any%20single%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20growing%20trade%20ties%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20other%20regions%2C%20India%20is%20working%20on%20strengthening%20its%20supply%20chain%20networks%20to%20ensure%20stability%20in%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20U.S.%20tariffs%20on%20Indian%20goods%20have%20remained%20relatively%20stable%20over%20the%20years%2C%20India's%20tariff%20policies%20have%20been%20more%20dynamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20that%20U.S.%20tariff%20rate%20on%20Indian%20goods%20increased%20from%202.72%20per%20cent%20in%202018%20to%203.91%20per%20cent%20in%202021%20before%20slightly%20decreasing%20to%203.83%20per%20cent%20in%202022.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20India's%20tariffs%20on%20U.S.%20imports%20have%20risen%20more%20significantly%2C%20from%2011.59%20per%20cent%20in%202018%20to%2015.30%20per%20cent%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20in%20tariff%20structures%20reflects%20a%20more%20assertive%20trade%20policy%20by%20India%2C%20aimed%20at%20balancing%20trade%20relations%20while%20protecting%20domestic%20industries.%20India%20has%20been%20focusing%20on%20adding%20value%20to%20its%20exports%2C%20shifting%20from%20raw%20materials%20to%20finished%20goods%20and%20high-value%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20not%20only%20enhances%20export%20earnings%20but%20also%20reduces%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20tariff%20hikes%20by%20ensuring%20that%20Indian%20goods%20remain%20competitive%20in%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20India%20is%20actively%20working%20on%20alternative%20trade%20routes%20that%20connect%20Europe%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%2C%20reducing%20logistical%20costs%20and%20improving%20efficiency.%20This%20restructured%20supply%20chain%20approach%20is%20expected%20to%20strengthen%20India's%20position%20in%20international%20trade%20despite%20global%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvera