ment-4-0-magnitude-earthquake-hit-delhi-ncr-7728059%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alexei%20Navalny's%20Wife%20Accuses%20Russia%20Of%20%26quot%3BHiding%20Truth%26quot%3B%20About%20His%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAlexei%20Navalny's%20widow%2C%20Yulia%20Navalnaya%2C%20has%20accused%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20of%20hiding%20the%20truth%20about%20Navalny's%20death%20in%20light%20of%20his%20first%20death%20anniversary%2C%20Al%20Jazeera%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl%20Jazeera%20noted%20that%20Alexei%20Navalny's%20death%20was%20officially%20attributed%20to%20natural%20causes%2C%20in%20an%20Arctic%20penal%20colony%20last%20February.%20Supporters%20of%20the%20late%20leading%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%20are%20commemorating%20the%20one-year%20anniversary%20of%20his%20death%20by%20visiting%20his%20grave%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Al%20Jazeera%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20to%20everyone%20who%20remembers%20Alexei%2C%20who%20talks%20about%20him%2C%20writes%20about%20him%2C%20who%20comes%20to%20the%20cemetery.%20I%20am%20grateful%20to%20those%20who%20have%20been%20supporting%20me%20this%20whole%20year.%20Your%20letters%2C%20your%20hugs%20when%20we%20meet%2C%20this%20is%20what%20does%20not%20let%20me%20forget%20why%20Alexei%20did%20this%20and%20why%20I'm%20doing%20this.%20If%20so%20many%20good%20people%20are%20on%20one%20side%2C%20we%20cannot%20help%20but%20win%26quot%3B%2C%20Yulia%20Navalnaya%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message%20as%20shared%20by%20Al%20Jazeera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20in%20the%20video%20message%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20now%20a%20year%20after%20his%20death%20he%20(Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin)%20is%20trying%20to%20erase%20Alexei's%20name%20from%20our%20memory%20to%20hide%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20murder%2C%20to%20make%20us%20come%20to%20terms%2C%20but%20he%20will%20not%20succeed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pain%