sinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-mexico-delayed-month-sheinbaum-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Canada.%20Trump%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20tariffs%20were%20intended%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20drug%20and%20border%20policy%2C%20particularly%20to%20stop%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrudeau-trump-tariffs-canadian-goods-paused-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaused%20the%20tariffs%20for%2030%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%203%20after%20both%20countries%20agreed%20to%20tougher%20border%20control%20measures%2C%20but%20he%20still%20promised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-reciprocal-tariffs-nations-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20goods%20imported%20from%20any%20country%20that%20levies%20tariffs%20on%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20posts%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Trump%20has%20maintained%20that%20%26quot%3Bdrugs%20are%20pouring%20into%20our%20Country%2C%20mostly%20through%20Mexico%2C%20at%20levels%20never%20seen%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20Guzman%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Harm%20Reduction%20Coalition%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20could%20make%20drug%20overdoses%20go%20up%20if%20they%20are%20successful%20in%20slowing%20the%20flow%20of%20illegal%20drugs%20into%20the%20country.%20Harm%20reduction%20generally%20refers%20to%20policies%20and%20practices%20that%20aim%20to%20minimize%20the%20negative%20health%2C%20social%2C%20and%20legal%20effects%20of%20drug%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20fear%20I%20had%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20negotiation%20to%20postpone%20the%20tariffs%2C%20immediately%2C%20my%20reaction%20was%2C%20'that%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20good%20for%20the%20folks%20that%20are%20impacted%20by%20both%20the%20war%20on%20drugs%2C%20but%20also%20by%20this%20tainted%20drug%20supply%2C'%26quot%3B%20Guzman%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuzman%20said%20that%20while%20slowing%20the%20rate%20of%20fentanyl%20entering%20the%20country%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20there%20is%20still%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20fentanyl%20that%20is%20produced%20inside%20the%20US%20that%20ends%20up%20on%20the%20streets.%20She%20said%20that%20disrupting%20the%20flow%20of%20drugs%20can%20create%20a%20situation%20where%20addicts%20are%20mixing%20drugs%20that%20they%20don't%20normally%20use%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20health%20risks%20and%20death.%20She%20said%20mixing%20drugs%20can%20lead%20to%20drug%20contamination%20where%20people%20might%20take%20drugs%20they%20aren't%20familiar%20with%20or%20are%20unaware%20that%20they%20are%20taking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20is%20more%20dangerous%2C%20because%20then%20the%20mixes%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20mixes%2C%20what%20it%20gets%20mixed%20with%2C%20puts%20people%20at%20risk%20of%20not%20just%20opiate%20overdoses%2C%20but%20also%20increase%20sedation%20that%20results%20in%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Guzman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuzman%20said%20that%20it%20is%20common%20for%20harm%20reduction%20workers%20to%20see%20spikes%20in%20overdose%20deaths%20in%20cities%20after%20local%20police%20do%20heavy%20drug%20takedowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20an%20interdiction%2C%20they%20start%20arresting%2C%20they%20say%20how%20much%20fentanyl%20have%20confiscated%2C%20and%20we%20very%20soon%20start%20seeing%20spikes%20of%20overdose%20deaths%2C%26quot%3B%20Guzman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229fe1868-2c55-4e5b-87f5-28582b8c81e8%5C%22%3EPutting%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20eggs%20on%20interdiction%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fentanyl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b25383eb4be2fff9a4cf5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20walking%20past%20anti-fentanyl%20campaign%20posters%20in%20Mexico%20City.%3Cp%3EYURI%20CORTEZ%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20critical%20of%20Mexico%2C%20saying%20that%20government%20needs%20to%20do%20more%20to%20recognize%20the%20ongoing%20fentanyl%20crisis%20impacting%20both%20countries.%20Guzman%20said%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20denial%26quot%3B%20from%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum's%20administration%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20influx%20of%20fentanyl%20from%20the%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20February%203%20that%20Mexico%20rejected%20claims%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20that%20Mexico%20colluded%20with%20criminal%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20United%20States%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20wanted%20to%20address%20the%20serious%20consumption%20of%20fentanyl%20in%20their%20country%2C%20they%20can%20combat%20the%20sale%20of%20narcotics%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20their%20main%20cities%2C%20which%20they%20don't%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheinbaum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaloxone%2C%20a%20drug%20that%20is%20used%20to%20reverse%20opioid%20overdoses%2C%20is%20a%20controlled%20substance%20in%20Mexico%2C%20where%20it%20is%20considered%20a%20psychoactive%20drug.%20Guzman%20said%20the%20country's%20refusal%20to%20recognize%20naloxone%20as%20a%20life-saving%20drug%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bputting%20all%20the%20eggs%20on%20interdiction%20and%20denies%20the%20fact%20that%20fentanyl%20is%20also%20taking%20lives%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20leans%20into%20fentanyl%20trafficking%20as%20a%20leading%20reason%20for%20its%20new%20tariffs%2C%20they%20have%20sometimes%20struggled%20to%20defend%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20on%20February%202%2C%20Kristin%20Welker%20asked%20Homeland%20Security%20Secretary%20Kristi%20Noem%20why%20Canada%20had%20been%20hit%20with%20more%20severe%20tariffs%20than%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20the%20United%20States%20punishing%20Canada%2C%20one%20of%20its%20closest%20allies%2C%20more%20than%20China%2C%20where%20fentanyl%20originates%3F%26quot%3B%20Welker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sent%20a%20message%20this%20week%20that%20we're%20not%20just%20going%20to%20enforce%20our%20southern%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Noem%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20put%20extra%20resources%20at%20that%20northern%20border%20as%20well.%20So%20Canada%20needs%20to%20come%20to%20the%20table.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20seized%20more%20than%2021%2C000%20pounds%20of%20fentanyl%20at%20the%20Mexican%20border%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency.%20The%20agency%20seized%2043%20pounds%20of%20fentanyl%20at%20the%20Canadian%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20also%20announced%20retaliatory%20tariffs%20if%20Trump's%20tariffs%20go%20into%20effect.%20Some%20tariffed%20goods%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-us-states-biggest-trade-partners-mexico-canada-china-imports-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20target%20Trump's%20political%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20covering%20items%20like%20Florida%20oranges%20and%20Kentucky%20bourbon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-fentanyl-crisis-mexico-canada-harm-reduction-expert-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739743723000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b2546d7bb3f854015d0d37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww