e%20assignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20generative%20AI%20technology%20becomes%20more%20integrated%20into%20students'%20lives%2C%20Salaka%20encourages%20parents%20to%20help%20them%20cultivate%20new%20critical%20thinking%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%20in%20time%2C%20AI%20work%20is%20going%20to%20be%20distinguishable%20from%20human%20sources%2C%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20for%20us%20to%20track%20the%20provenance%20of%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Salaka%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20disinformation%2C%20deepfakes%2C%20all%20of%20these%20things%20are%20going%20to%20become%20much%20more%20prevalent%20as%20we%20move%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20learn%20to%20start%20asking%20questions%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20that%20source%20valid%3F%20What%20is%20the%20rationale%20behind%20that%20source%20to%20say%2C%20hey%2C%20this%20is%20true%3F%20Are%20there%20other%20sources%20that%20corroborate%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20AI%20tools%20are%20beginning%20to%20display%20sources%20in%20their%20outputs.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-deep-research-launch-chatgpt-ai-agent-deepseek-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20launched%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20research%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20new%20agent%20that%20conducts%20extensive%20research%20online%2C%20synthesizes%20it%2C%20and%20documents%20its%20outputs%20with%20%26quot%3Bclear%20citations%20and%20a%20summary%20of%20its%20thinking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Anthropic%20launched%20Citations%2C%20an%20API%20feature%20that%20lets%20its%20chatbot%2C%20Claude%2C%20provide%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20references%20to%20the%20exact%20sentences%20and%20passages%20it%20uses%20to%20generate%20responses.%26quot%3B%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%2C%20Perplexity%2C%20also%20includes%20footnotes%20linking%20to%20original%20sources%20in%20every%20answer%20it%20generates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20many%20parents%20who%20are%20apprehensive%20about%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20according%20to%20Audrey%20Wisch%2C%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curiouscardinals.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurious%20Cardinals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tutoring%20and%20mentorship%20network%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20Over%20the%20past%2020%20months%2C%20Wisch%20has%20taught%20over%2075%20workshops%20for%20parents%20on%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20optimize%20their%20productivity.%20Before%20the%20workshops%2C%20she%20asks%20parents%20to%20fill%20out%20a%20registration%20form%20detailing%20their%20AI%20anxieties%2C%20among%20other%20points%2C%20and%20has%20collected%20more%20than%202%2C000%20responses%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20this%20anxiety%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20screw%20up%20their%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there's%20just%20so%20much%20fear%20and%20there's%20so%20much%20misunderstanding.%20I%20think%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20fears%20are%20cutting%20corners%20%E2%80%94%20will%20my%20kid%20not%20know%20how%20to%20write%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%20Cardinals%20pairs%20students%20in%20kindergarten%20through%2012th%20grade%20with%20mentors%20to%20help%20them%20with%20schoolwork%2C%20pursue%20passion%20projects%2C%20or%20provide%20career%20guidance%2C%20and%20has%20incorporated%20AI%20education%20into%20those%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWisch%20said%20that%20a%20few%20parents%20have%20started%20asking%20for%20AI%20mentoring%2C%20too.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20two%20mentors%20who%20are%20teaching%20moms%20AI%20one%20on%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20love%20is%20seeing%20these%20women%20become%20very%20digitally%20empowered%20who%20otherwise%20are%20digitally%20insecure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-