l%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20loaned%20my%20sister%20money%20whenever%20she%20needed%20it.%20I%20helped%20her%20purchase%20her%20first%20car%2C%20put%20her%20on%20my%20phone%20plan%20and%20often%20covered%20the%20monthly%20bill%20alone%2C%20made%20sure%20she%20could%20attend%20the%20annual%20trip%20our%20cousins%20put%20together%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20done%20it%20because%20I'm%20her%20older%20sister%2C%20and%20she%20has%20usually%20agreed%20to%20pay%20me%20back%20eventually.%20I%20never%20hassled%20her%20about%20it%2C%20as%20she%20was%20young%2C%20struggling%2C%20and%20not%20in%20a%20place%20to%20repay%20me%20yet.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecently%2C%20my%20sister%20landed%20a%20high-paying%20job%2C%20earning%20more%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20family%20combined.%20While%20I'm%20married%20with%20a%20kid%2C%20she's%20unattached%20and%20has%20no%20real%20responsibilities%20beyond%20herself.%20I'm%20proud%20of%20her%20and%20don't%20resent%20her%20success.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20realized%2C%20though%2C%20that%20if%20she%20paid%20back%20even%20some%20of%20the%20money%20she%20owes%20me%2C%20it%20would%20really%20help%20my%20family.%20I%20tallied%20how%20much%20she's%20borrowed%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20excluding%20all%20the%20things%20we%20never%20explicitly%20called%20loans%2C%20the%20total%20comes%20to%20%245%2C000.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESince%20she%20started%20making%20more%20money%2C%20I've%20mentioned%20her%20paying%20back%20some%20of%20what%20she's%20borrowed%20from%20me.%20Her%20response%20is%20always%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20yeah.%20I%20get%20it.%20You've%20helped%20me%20a%20lot%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20she%20seems%20to%20have%20completely%20forgotten%20that%20these%20were%20always%20supposed%20to%20be%20loans%2C%20not%20gifts.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20her%20credit%2C%20since%20she's%20been%20earning%20more%2C%20she%20pays%20her%20share%20of%20the%20phone%20bill%20and%20covers%20her%20portion%20of%20the%20cousin's%20trip%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20same%20as%20paying%20her%20debts.%20How%20do%20I%20ask%20her%20to%20pay%20me%20%245%2C000%20for%20loans%20going%20back%2010%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerous%20to%20a%20Fault%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Generous%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can%20think%20of%20few%20trickier%20interpersonal%20conflicts%20to%20navigate%20than%20disagreements%20over%20whether%20a%20financial%20boost%20from%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20was%20a%20gift%20or%20a%20loan.%20We%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20spell%20these%20things%20out%20early%20on%2C%20we%20avoid%20arguments%20or%20awkwardness%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20as%20cases%20like%20yours%20demonstrate%2C%20if%20enough%20small%20amounts%20of%20money%20have%20been%20exchanged%20over%20a%20long%20period%2C%20and%20there's%20familial%20comfort%20involved%2C%20everyone%20will%20still%20often%20(and%20conveniently)%20remember%20things%20differently.%20This%20isn't%20to%20say%20your%20sister%20will%20disagree%20with%20you%20if%20you%20ask%20her%20for%20repayment%20outright%2C%20but%20her%20dismissive%20response%20to%20your%20nudging%20suggests%20she%20might.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20your%20sister%20is%20doing%20this%20intentionally%2C%20or%20maybe%20it's%20an%20honest%20misunderstanding%2C%20or%20perhaps%20it's%20simply%20a%20difference%20in%20worldview.%20She%20may%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20how%20family%20takes%20care%20of%20each%20other%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20you%20really%20ever%20planned%20on%20making%20her%20repay%20you.%20I'm%20positive%20I%20will%20receive%20at%20least%20a%20few%20messages%20from%20readers%20offended%20by%20my%20suggestion%20that%20this%20could%20be%20a%20reasonable%20thing%20for%20your%20sister%20to%20feel%2C%20but%20I%20will%20also%20receive%20several%20upset%20that%20you%20ever%20expected%20your%20little%20sister%20to%20repay%20you%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20The%20truth%20is%2C%20it's%20simply%20a%20difference%20in%20value%20systems%2C%20and%20a%20valid%20one%20at%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20your%20sister's%20reasons%20for%20failing%20to%20pay%20you%20back%2C%20they%20have%20little%20bearing%20on%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%20about%20it.%20Instead%2C%20you%20must%20base%20your%20decision%20on%20your%20desired%20outcomes.%20Obviously%2C%20you%20want%20your%20money%20back.%20Who%20wouldn't%20appreciate%20a%20%245%2C000%20cash%20injection%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20since%20you%20both%20agreed%20these%20were%20loans%20back%20when%20you%20gave%20them%20to%20her%2C%20she%20owes%20you.%20However%2C%20if%20she%20disagrees%20with%20you%2C%20you%20must%20ask%20yourself%20what%20you're%20willing%20to%20risk%20if%20you%20keep%20pushing%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20what%20you%20risk%20by%20dropping%20it.%20Are%20you%20OK%20with%20hurting%20your%20relationship%20with%20your%20sister%20if%20it%20gets%20you%20the%20money%20you're%20owed%3F%20But%20also%2C%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20forget%20the%20debt%20and%20move%20forward%2C%20are%20you%20OK%20remaining%20quiet%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20treated%20you%20this%20way%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20decide%20to%20press%20the%20issue%2C%20you%20must%20ensure%20your%20sister%20is%20actually%20opposed%20to%20paying%20you%20back%20%E2%80%94%20no%20casual%20references%20to%20old%20loans%20or%20passive-aggressive%20comments%20about%20what%20she%20ought%20to%20do%20with%20her%20new%20spending%20power.%20Tell%20your%20sister%20outright%20that%20you're%20calling%20in%20her%20loans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20understand%20being%20this%20direct%20in%20a%20relationship%20is%20scary.%20Shining%20a%20light%20on%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20awkward%20exchanges%20over%20unpaid%20phone%20bills%20and%20generously%20covered%20vacation%20rentals%20will%20probably%20reveal%20many%20other%20things%20best%20left%20in%20the%20past.%20Being%20this%20clear%20about%20your%20expectations%20will%20also%20require%20you%20to%20show%20your%20financial%20hand%20to%20your%20younger%20sibling.%20A%20sibling%20you%20have%20spent%20years%20taking%20care%20of%20will%20now%20see%20how%20much%20%245%2C000%20means%20to%20you%20%E2%80%94%20more%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20than%20that%20amount%20of%20money%20means%20to%20her%20at%20this%20point.%20This%20may%20feel%20humbling%20to%20you%20as%20a%20big%20sister%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20get%20far%20without%20honesty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20should%20also%20consider%20being%20creative%20about%20how%20she%20repays%20you.%20Not%20even%20people%20we%20consider%20wealthy%20necessarily%20have%20%245%2C000%20lying%20around%20to%20hand%20over%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice.%20You%20might%20suggest%20your%20sister%20pay%20you%20in%20installments%2C%20cover%20the%20entire%20phone%20bill%20for%20a%20while%2C%20or%20pay%20your%20share%20of%20the%20cousins'%20trip%20until%20she's%20repaid%20her%20debt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20long%20as%20you're%20both%20clear%20on%20the%20plan%20and%20keep%20track%20of%20where%20she's%20at%20in%20her%20repayment%2C%20this%20could%20be%20an%20excellent%20way%20for%20her%20to%20ease%20your%20life%20in%20the%20same%20way%20you%20eased%20hers%20over%20the%20years%20without%20hitting%20her%20wallet%20too%20hard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20reading%20t